ữ từ tự cảnh văn - 抒辭自警文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-ng%C3%A2m/poem-A7bqmZ6MNjzOfeJcMvCNqg">Trường ngâm - 長吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%A1-L%C3%A3m/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Nh%E1%BB%8B-Tr%C6%B0ng-phu-nh%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-tmFAlCRKyVL-ZQWITq9bGg">Vịnh Nhị Trưng phu nhân từ - 詠二徵夫人祠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%A1-L%C3%A3m/author-9ppkdEWSUlq0gOg71v0QIQ">Trần Bá Lãm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Gia-K%E1%BB%B7/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-gi%E1%BA%A3i-t%E1%BB%AD-phu-th%C3%AA/poem-nvWXldPQFCgPzVvH2hpTWw">Vương giải tử phu thê - 王解子夫婦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Gia-K%E1%BB%B7/author-WRSP543j56aeSlO4dZfsBQ">Ngô Gia Kỷ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
